<div class="container" *ngIf="isShipper == false">
    <div class="row slide-shipper">
        <div class="col-sm-12 ">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <h1>Easy Shopping</h1>
                <h2>Become a shipper</h2>
                <p>There is a thousand orders a day to do shipping and it is still raising day by day. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="background-color:#425161; color:white">
        <h1 style="text-align:center">Why Us?</h1>
        <div class="col-md-12" style="max-height:500px">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div style="text-align:right">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/empty.png" style="height:500px" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 shipper-side-content">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/icon_Mobility.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h1>Mobility</h1>
                        <p>By using phone to use this app, the worry of hard to moving is long gone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/234171-market-and-economics.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h1>Huge Market</h1>
                        <p>Easy Shopping provides a huge market with a thousand order a day.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="position:relative">
        <h1 class="shipper-header">Be a shipper</h1>
        <div style="padding: 0 10% 0 10%">
            <div class="row announcement_row col-md-4" style="text-align:center">
                <div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/register.png" class="announcement_img" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <h2>Register</h2>
                        <div style="text-align:left">
                            <p>To become a part of us you must register to be a shipper first.</p>
                            <button style="text-align:center" [routerLink]="['/shippers/shipper-register']" *ngIf="isApplied == false">Apply now</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row announcement_row col-md-4" style="text-align:center">
                <div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/icon-803718_960_720.png" class="announcement_img" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <h2>Approve</h2>
                        <p>After reviewing your CV we will activate your account. An activated account can use use full of shipper's functions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="announcement_row col-md-4" style="text-align:center">
                <div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <img src="~/Content/img/shipper/shipper.png" class="announcement_img" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <h2>Be a shipper</h2>
                        <p>
                            Shipper will use the mobile app to take orders which have specific information. We are providing many functions
                            that help shipper can easily take and ship orders.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
